Brazil Court Voting on Granting Rights to Gay Couples

-- B y   I u r i   D a n t a s
-- 
2011-05-05T21:38:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-05/brazil-court-voting-on-granting-rights-to-gay-couples-correct-.html
(Corrects to say court is still voting.)  Brazil ’s  Supreme Court  is in the
process of voting on whether homosexual partners can form civil
unions, enjoying the same legal rights as heterosexuals,
according to a statement on the court’s website.  To contact the reporter on this story:
